Nutrient data for: TRIDENT GUM PEPPERMINT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210059581
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sweeteners (sorbitol, isomalt, maltitol syrup, maltitol, aspartame, acesulfame K), gum base, bulking agent (E 170), flavourings, humectant (E 422), thickener (E 414), emulsifiers (E 472 a, sunflower lecithin), colours (E 171, E 133), glazing agent (E 903), antioxidant (E 321). Contains a source of phenylalanine. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect.. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
